DRDGold of South Africa Says 8 Mineworkers Die, 37 Injured in Bus Accident

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-03-18T06:23:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-18/drdgold-of-south-africa-says-8-mineworkers-die-37-injured-in-bus-accident.html
  DRDGold Ltd. (DRD)  said eight mineworkers
died and about 37 were injured in a bus accident at its
Blyvooruitzicht mine near Carletonville in  South Africa  today.  The cause of the accident is not yet known, the company
said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  